<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1104</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ qiú nǐ jiǎn xuǎn wǒ de qīn rén, jiù xiàng nǐ jiǎn xuǎn wǒ yī yàng.
 zhǔ qiú nǐ zhěng jiù wǒ de qīn rén, jiù xiàng nǐ zhěng jiù wǒ yī yàng.
 zhǔ qiú nǐ tí xǐng wǒ de qīn rén, jiù xiàng nǐ tí xǐng wǒ yī yàng.
 shì shàng wàn shì jiē xū kōng, xìn yé sū de rén jiā zài tiān shàng.
 zhǔ a rú guǒ nà yī tiān nǐ jiē wǒ men dōu huí jiā xiāng,
 kàn bù dào wǒ de qīn rén, wǒ de xīn hái shì yōu shāng.
 liǎn shàng yě bù huì yǒu xiào róng, gèng bù huì yǒu róng guāng.
 qiú nǐ kuài zhěng jiù wǒ de qīn rén, bù guǎn tā men zài hé fāng.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ qiú nǐ jiǎn xuǎn wǒ de qīn rén 迦南1104</title>
</song>